name: CXHandle
desc: A means by which a call recipient can be reached, such as a phone number or email address.

items.name: s CXCallObserver
items.desc: A programmatic interface for an object that manages a list of active calls and observes call changes.

items.name: ocol CXCallObserverDelegate
items.desc: A collection of methods that are called by a call observer object when a call changes state.
